A Cloudflare Worker generated from the Artemis `cf-worker-app` template.

## Develop

```bash
pnpm install
pnpm dev          # wrangler dev — serves http://localhost:8787
```

- `GET /` — hello route
- `GET /healthz` — liveness probe: `200 {"version": "<tag>"}`

## Gates (run before pushing; CI runs them too)

```bash
pnpm lint         # biome ci .
pnpm typecheck    # tsc --noEmit
pnpm test         # vitest run --coverage
pnpm build        # wrangler dry-run build
```

CI runs the shared Artemis pipelines (`ci`, `security`{% if visibility == 'public' %}, `codeql`{% endif %}) on every PR. See
[docs/runbooks/deploy.md](docs/runbooks/deploy.md) and
[docs/runbooks/rollback.md](docs/runbooks/rollback.md) for operations.

## Deploy

Production deploys are tag-driven and human-approved (never by an agent). Preview deploys
run per-PR. See the deploy runbook.
